\series bold

\begin_inset Formula $\boldsymbol{w}=(1/4,3/4)$
\end_inset

 
\series default
and 
\begin_inset Formula $p=2$
\end_inset

.
 Formulate the weighted norm problem 
\begin_inset Formula $\mathrm{P}(\boldsymbol{w},p)$
\end_inset

 and find all optimal solutions to this problem.
\end_layout

